00:22:42.559 --> 00:22:45.190
Isaac sowed in famine and reaped a

00:22:45.190 --> 00:22:45.200
hundredfold

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:48.390
that same year. Look at all the

00:22:48.400 --> 00:22:50.789
things the Lord always does for his

00:22:50.799 --> 00:22:53.190
people for a way out. He doesn't

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:55.430
catch his

00:22:55.440 --> 00:22:57.430
children off guard. It says he's never

00:22:57.440 --> 00:22:59.430
seen the righteous forsaken or his

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:02.310
seed begging bread. If God did it in

00:23:02.320 --> 00:23:05.590
the Old Testament for his kids,

00:23:05.600 --> 00:23:07.830
how much more will he do it for you in

00:23:07.840 --> 00:23:10.230
his new covenant with us? He

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:12.950
loves us.

00:23:15.600 --> 00:23:17.190
If he took care of them

00:23:17.200 --> 00:23:18.870
in the old covenant, he'll take care of

00:23:18.880 --> 00:23:20.789
us in the new. I'm just

00:23:20.799 --> 00:23:22.870
believing with all my heart that he's

00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:24.549
going to provide for us. I'm not

00:23:24.559 --> 00:23:25.909
believing that we're going to have the

00:23:25.919 --> 00:23:27.990
rug yanked out from underneath us

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:29.990
and we'll be going, "Man, woe is me."We're

00:23:29.990 --> 00:23:30.000
the head and not

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:32.149
the tail.

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:41.510
I believe with all my

00:23:41.520 --> 00:23:43.029
heart that he's going to take care of

00:23:43.039 --> 00:23:45.669
his kids. I

00:23:45.679 --> 00:23:47.750
always want to come across with hope

00:23:47.760 --> 00:23:50.149
and faith, believing for

00:23:50.149 --> 00:23:50.159
an

00:23:50.159 --> 00:23:51.990
"exceedingly abundantly above all that we

00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:54.230
dare ask or think"kind of God, rather than a

00:23:54.230 --> 00:23:54.240
God who is

00:23:54.240 --> 00:23:56.070
out there beating

00:23:56.080 --> 00:23:57.669
people upside the head because he's angry.

00:23:57.679 --> 00:24:00.390
God is not mad at us. Like I

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:02.549
told you, people are going to call this

00:24:02.559 --> 00:24:05.110
a great Ichabod. That's what the Lord

00:24:05.120 --> 00:24:07.590
showed me: people

00:24:07.600 --> 00:24:09.350
are going to say, "This is a great

00:24:09.350 --> 00:24:09.360
Ichabod"when

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:11.029
all

00:24:11.039 --> 00:24:12.950
this starts to take place, that

00:24:12.950 --> 00:24:12.960
he's

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:14.710
departed and left America.

00:24:16.880 --> 00:24:18.950
But I'm telling you, he

00:24:18.960 --> 00:24:20.789
said, "I never leave you nor will I ever

00:24:20.799 --> 00:24:22.870
forsake you. Lo, into the earth,

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:24.710
I'll be with you always."He's in us, he

00:24:24.720 --> 00:24:26.230
sent us the Holy Spirit, and he's dwelling

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:28.710
on the inside of us. Even in our

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:31.590
darkest hours, he's there.

00:24:34.320 --> 00:24:36.310
Sometimes we go through tests

00:24:36.320 --> 00:24:38.070
because we're

00:24:38.080 --> 00:24:39.750
going through the refiner's fire.

00:24:42.080 --> 00:24:43.830
What the Lord showed me

00:24:43.840 --> 00:24:45.669
is coming

00:24:45.669 --> 00:24:45.679
is

00:24:45.679 --> 00:24:47.510
a cleaning; it's

00:24:47.520 --> 00:24:49.990
the potter's wheel. I talk

00:24:50.000 --> 00:24:52.070
about the clay on

00:24:52.080 --> 00:24:53.990
the potter's wheel all the time.

00:24:55.600 --> 00:24:57.269
It's a very

00:24:57.279 --> 00:25:00.230
serious time that we're coming into.

00:25:00.240 --> 00:25:02.630
The people who are listening to him,

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:04.390
following the Holy

00:25:04.400 --> 00:25:06.549
Ghost, and

00:25:06.559 --> 00:25:09.110
seeking him daily

00:25:09.110 --> 00:25:09.120
will

00:25:09.120 --> 00:25:10.789
get revelation knowledge

00:25:10.799 --> 00:25:12.230
and you're going to hear whether

00:25:12.240 --> 00:25:13.830
what you're supposed to put your money

00:25:13.840 --> 00:25:15.750
into and how to invest,

00:25:15.760 --> 00:25:17.830
how to protect your

00:25:17.840 --> 00:25:19.909
family,

00:25:19.919 --> 00:25:21.430
and

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:23.269
being frugal with what the Lord's giving

00:25:23.279 --> 00:25:25.190
you. It's not a time to be stupid with

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:27.669
your money; it's a time to be wise and

00:25:27.679 --> 00:25:30.230
listening for him to be

00:25:30.240 --> 00:25:33.430
telling you to do things:

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:35.110
helping your church out, helping out

00:25:35.120 --> 00:25:37.190
your fellow brother. I

00:25:37.200 --> 00:25:39.350
really believe with all my

00:25:39.350 --> 00:25:39.360
heart—and

00:25:39.360 --> 00:25:41.190
I'm not a financial

00:25:41.190 --> 00:25:41.200
adviser—I'll

00:25:41.200 --> 00:25:42.470
say that a thousand

00:25:42.480 --> 00:25:44.549
times. I am not someone who is out

00:25:44.559 --> 00:25:46.310
here to tell you how to invest

00:25:46.320 --> 00:25:48.070
your money, but he tells me things and

00:25:48.080 --> 00:25:50.230
shows me certain things.

00:25:50.230 --> 00:25:50.240
I

00:25:50.240 --> 00:25:52.549
believe with all my heart that

00:25:52.559 --> 00:25:54.870
if you're listening to him,

00:25:54.880 --> 00:26:00.310
there's going to be, like I

00:26:00.320 --> 00:26:03.430
said, I saw a number with 2%. It wasn't

00:26:03.440 --> 00:26:05.110
a lot of people, but there was a turnaround

00:26:05.120 --> 00:26:06.470
of things that will happen

00:26:06.480 --> 00:26:08.549
for folks if they're believing for him

00:26:08.559 --> 00:26:12.230
to take care of them. So, there

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:14.630
you go on that.

00:26:14.640 --> 00:26:17.510
Edward, your potter friend,

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:20.390
he gave you a super

00:26:20.400 --> 00:26:22.950
thanks and wanted to ask how long it was

00:26:22.960 --> 00:26:24.950
when the angel gave you the number of

00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:26.070
days,

00:26:26.070 --> 00:26:26.080
or

00:26:26.080 --> 00:26:27.190
how it happened.

00:26:27.200 --> 00:26:29.590
The angel... okay, I was in

00:26:29.600 --> 00:26:30.149
a dream

00:26:30.149 --> 00:26:30.159
where

00:26:30.159 --> 00:26:33.590
he said 569 days.

00:26:33.600 --> 00:26:36.549
That happened on October

00:26:36.559 --> 00:26:38.950
2nd.

00:26:38.960 --> 00:26:40.149
569 days.

00:26:44.159 --> 00:26:47.750
Whenever I had the dream,

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:49.590
an angel came to me

00:26:49.600 --> 00:26:51.430
and he said, 'There

00:26:51.430 --> 00:26:51.440
is

00:26:51.440 --> 00:26:53.510
great judgment

00:26:53.510 --> 00:26:53.520
coming.'He

00:26:53.520 --> 00:26:58.070
said, 'In 569 days,

00:26:58.080 --> 00:26:59.269
there will be great judgment

00:26:59.279 --> 00:27:01.190
coming, but you are to pray

00:27:01.190 --> 00:27:01.200
and

00:27:01.200 --> 00:27:04.149
intercede.'I

00:27:04.159 --> 00:27:06.630
asked the angel in the dream,

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:08.950
'What is coming?'and he said,

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:10.870
'I cannot tell you.'He said, 'The Lord

00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:12.549
tells me you have to intercede and he

00:27:12.559 --> 00:27:14.390
will give it to you in pieces. He'll

00:27:14.400 --> 00:27:16.230
tell you in part and

00:27:16.240 --> 00:27:17.430
give you

00:27:17.440 --> 00:27:21.110
more as you pray.'So he told

00:27:21.120 --> 00:27:23.830
me it would be 569 days.

00:27:23.830 --> 00:27:23.840
That

00:27:23.840 --> 00:27:28.149
came about in August, and then

00:27:28.159 --> 00:27:30.390
the Lord told me, 'Brandon, I'm

00:27:30.400 --> 00:27:33.269
giving more time. I'm extending more

00:27:33.269 --> 00:27:33.279
time.'So

00:27:33.279 --> 00:27:36.070
whenever

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:38.070
I'm seeing and hearing the Lord,

00:27:38.080 --> 00:27:40.230
like I said, it's just like

00:27:40.230 --> 00:27:40.240
when

00:27:40.240 --> 00:27:42.149
Abraham came before the Lord and was

00:27:42.159 --> 00:27:44.870
asking for Sodom and Gomorrah if

00:27:44.880 --> 00:27:47.190
there be 50 righteous. He kept going

00:27:47.200 --> 00:27:48.310
down and down, all the way

00:27:48.320 --> 00:27:50.870
to 10. Do you see how even in the old

00:27:50.880 --> 00:27:53.909
covenant, Abraham was a

00:27:53.919 --> 00:27:55.669
friend of God? Look how much grace he gave

00:27:55.679 --> 00:27:57.990
even to Sodom and

00:27:58.000 --> 00:28:00.149
Gomorrah. When you read the

00:28:00.159 --> 00:28:02.870
whole passage,

00:28:02.870 --> 00:28:02.880
it

00:28:02.880 --> 00:28:05.110
was terrible what was going

00:28:05.120 --> 00:28:07.909
on there. Yet God was willing even at that

00:28:07.919 --> 00:28:10.710
time to give mercy and intercede because

00:28:10.720 --> 00:28:13.510
Abraham was interceding for them. And

00:28:13.520 --> 00:28:15.430
look what he did. He was able to say,

00:28:15.440 --> 00:28:17.510
'Listen, if there be just

00:28:17.510 --> 00:28:17.520
10,'and

00:28:17.520 --> 00:28:19.750
there wasn't. I'm sure he was

00:28:19.760 --> 00:28:21.350
thinking, 'Surely there is more

00:28:21.360 --> 00:28:23.110
than that in

00:28:23.120 --> 00:28:24.630
there.'I

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:26.310
bet even if he went down

00:28:26.320 --> 00:28:28.630
to one and it was just

00:28:28.630 --> 00:28:28.640
Lot—would

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:30.870
you spare the city just for Lot?

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:32.870
But he didn't go that far.

00:28:32.880 --> 00:28:34.310
Maybe that's all he felt in his

00:28:34.320 --> 00:28:36.230
spirit to go

00:28:36.230 --> 00:28:36.240
to.

00:28:36.240 --> 00:28:38.789
I believe

00:28:38.799 --> 00:28:40.389
with all my

00:28:40.389 --> 00:28:40.399
heart—going

00:28:40.399 --> 00:28:41.669
back to this because I keep going on

00:28:41.679 --> 00:28:44.950
these rabbit trails—when you

00:28:44.960 --> 00:28:48.149
are praying and interceding,

00:28:49.760 --> 00:28:51.590
you don't realize how much

00:28:51.600 --> 00:28:54.230
authority you have. When you

00:28:54.240 --> 00:28:56.710
spend time with the Lord and sit in

00:28:56.720 --> 00:28:59.590
his lap, curl up, and

00:28:59.600 --> 00:29:02.149
just love on him and worship him, you realize how

00:29:02.159 --> 00:29:04.389
much of a soft daddy he really is to his

00:29:04.399 --> 00:29:07.590
kids. He's not an ogre. He's not up

00:29:07.600 --> 00:29:09.909
there as a mad God beating

00:29:09.919 --> 00:29:12.870
people with rods. He

00:29:12.880 --> 00:29:14.710
loves on you.

00:29:14.720 --> 00:29:16.070
I'll come in and

00:29:16.070 --> 00:29:16.080
say,

00:29:16.080 --> 00:29:17.510
'Hey, Dad, I'm coming into your

00:29:17.510 --> 00:29:17.520
courts.'I

00:29:17.520 --> 00:29:19.669
petition him in

00:29:19.679 --> 00:29:21.029
his courts all the time.

00:29:21.039 --> 00:29:23.350
'Father, how's your day

00:29:23.350 --> 00:29:23.360
today?'and

00:29:23.360 --> 00:29:25.669
he'll go, 'Hey, Brandon, it's good

00:29:25.679 --> 00:29:27.110
to see you.'It's just the way

00:29:27.120 --> 00:29:28.789
we talk. I know he never

00:29:28.799 --> 00:29:30.389
leaves us or forsakes us, but

00:29:30.389 --> 00:29:30.399
he's

00:29:30.399 --> 00:29:32.950
excited because the way I petition him

00:29:32.960 --> 00:29:34.549
is by going into his courts and having

00:29:34.559 --> 00:29:36.470
fellowship in his

00:29:36.480 --> 00:29:38.310
throne room, just going in

00:29:38.320 --> 00:29:39.990
there, talking to him, and

00:29:40.000 --> 00:29:42.149
being his buddy. I want to be God's

00:29:42.159 --> 00:29:43.350
friend.

00:29:43.360 --> 00:29:44.710
You

00:29:44.720 --> 00:29:46.950
just got a super thanks from Sean. He

00:29:46.950 --> 00:29:46.960
asked,

00:29:46.960 --> 00:29:49.669
'When you have

00:29:49.679 --> 00:29:50.950
your personal time with the Lord, do you

00:29:50.960 --> 00:29:52.789
speak out loud to him or is it all

00:29:52.799 --> 00:29:54.630
inside? Should we pray

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:56.549
out loud? Peace be to

00:29:56.549 --> 00:29:56.559
you.'Yes,

00:29:56.559 --> 00:29:58.710
I speak to him

00:29:58.720 --> 00:30:00.389
like I'm talking to

00:30:00.399 --> 00:30:03.830
you right now. I'm not

00:30:03.840 --> 00:30:05.350
religious

00:30:05.360 --> 00:30:07.909
about this stuff. I think people

00:30:07.919 --> 00:30:11.669
treat God

00:30:11.679 --> 00:30:13.590
like the priests and the

00:30:13.600 --> 00:30:17.269
Pharisees; it's weird.

00:30:17.279 --> 00:30:19.510
Church doesn't have to be weird;

00:30:19.520 --> 00:30:21.590
Jesus is personal. When you start

00:30:21.600 --> 00:30:23.110
getting real with God, God gets real

00:30:23.120 --> 00:30:25.590
with you. People are always trying to be

00:30:25.600 --> 00:30:27.909
all religious and

00:30:27.919 --> 00:30:29.830
everything. Yes, we reverence him

00:30:29.830 --> 00:30:29.840
and

00:30:29.840 --> 00:30:31.590
respect him, and he

00:30:31.590 --> 00:30:31.600
is

00:30:31.600 --> 00:30:34.549
holy, but God is our Father

00:30:34.559 --> 00:30:37.669
and he loves us. We're

00:30:41.679 --> 00:30:43.350
his children. It

00:30:43.360 --> 00:30:45.350
says, 'You are my children.'How do

00:30:45.360 --> 00:30:47.430
you look at your children?

00:30:47.440 --> 00:30:48.789
You say, 'Please come up and crawl

00:30:48.799 --> 00:30:50.310
on my lap. I want to love on you.'That's

00:30:50.310 --> 00:30:50.320
how He

00:30:50.320 --> 00:30:52.149
is to

00:30:52.159 --> 00:30:54.470
us. He's our Father, he loves us, and

00:30:54.480 --> 00:30:56.710
people don't realize he's not mad.

00:30:56.720 --> 00:30:58.789
He just wants us to be his

00:30:58.799 --> 00:30:59.590
kids.

00:30:59.600 --> 00:31:01.830
Then someone

00:31:01.830 --> 00:31:01.840
asked

00:31:01.840 --> 00:31:05.110
if you might do

00:31:05.110 --> 00:31:05.120
an

00:31:05.120 --> 00:31:06.870
online Bible study.

00:31:06.870 --> 00:31:06.880
I'll

00:31:06.880 --> 00:31:08.710
pray about it.

00:31:11.520 --> 00:31:14.310
I'm not a big theology person.

00:31:14.320 --> 00:31:16.070
Like I've told you all,

00:31:16.080 --> 00:31:17.750
I have learning disabilities that

00:31:17.760 --> 00:31:19.190
I've overcome with reading and

00:31:19.200 --> 00:31:21.750
writing. So I listen to a lot

00:31:21.760 --> 00:31:23.669
of my Bible. I push the

00:31:23.679 --> 00:31:25.350
button and it plays,

00:31:25.360 --> 00:31:26.950
and I follow along.

00:31:26.960 --> 00:31:29.510
I'm just

00:31:29.520 --> 00:31:31.430
being open and real with you

00:31:31.430 --> 00:31:31.440
all.

00:31:31.440 --> 00:31:34.070
As far as studying the

00:31:34.080 --> 00:31:37.269
Word, I love to read the book of

00:31:37.279 --> 00:31:40.389
Ephesians. I love

00:31:40.399 --> 00:31:43.269
Hebrews,

00:31:43.279 --> 00:31:46.310
Romans, and James.

00:31:46.320 --> 00:31:48.310
I read them over and over

00:31:48.320 --> 00:31:50.149
again, letting the Bible read to me.

00:31:51.200 --> 00:31:52.789
You got an interesting comment from

00:31:52.799 --> 00:31:55.029
Anita. She said, 'Here in Australia,

00:31:55.039 --> 00:31:56.470
banks aren't allowing people to get

00:31:56.480 --> 00:31:58.070
cash out, many bank branches are

00:31:58.080 --> 00:32:00.070
closing, and we're losing ATMs.

00:32:00.080 --> 00:32:01.590
Some people have to travel over

00:32:01.600 --> 00:32:02.950
two hours to get to a

00:32:02.950 --> 00:32:02.960
bank.'It's

00:32:02.960 --> 00:32:05.750
just the beginning.

00:32:05.760 --> 00:32:07.269
The Lord told me—remember when I told

00:32:07.279 --> 00:32:12.470
you all I saw the flag on

00:32:12.480 --> 00:32:15.110
the pole and the dollar turn?

00:32:15.120 --> 00:32:17.430
It was a hundred-dollar bill on the pole,

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:19.110
split down the middle.

00:32:19.120 --> 00:32:21.590
It was moving, but it

00:32:21.600 --> 00:32:23.430
started to fade out.

00:32:23.440 --> 00:32:25.509
I really believe

00:32:25.519 --> 00:32:27.750
that's what we're about to see. I

00:32:27.760 --> 00:32:30.470
believe when Saudi Arabia starts to go

00:32:30.480 --> 00:32:33.190
full swing with the BRICS nations and we

00:32:33.200 --> 00:32:37.029
see all those countries from the

00:32:37.039 --> 00:32:39.990
UAE and Egypt

00:32:40.000 --> 00:32:42.070
join,

00:32:42.080 --> 00:32:44.149
80% of all the oil

00:32:44.159 --> 00:32:45.750
wealth of the world will join the

00:32:45.760 --> 00:32:48.789
BRICS nations by January

00:32:48.789 --> 00:32:48.799
1st.

00:32:48.799 --> 00:32:51.590
That's huge because the

00:32:51.590 --> 00:32:51.600
petrodollar

00:32:51.600 --> 00:32:53.350
is in trouble if that happens.

00:32:53.360 --> 00:32:56.870
I'm not here to...

00:32:56.880 --> 00:32:58.070
what, babe?

00:32:58.080 --> 00:32:59.110
I thought you were looking

00:32:59.120 --> 00:32:59.909
at me.

00:32:59.919 --> 00:33:01.590
No, I'm just looking at you

00:33:01.590 --> 00:33:01.600
because

00:33:01.600 --> 00:33:02.789
you're looking at me, and I don't want to

00:33:02.799 --> 00:33:03.990
say anything because I'm on a live

00:33:03.990 --> 00:33:04.000
stream.

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:05.110
I'm going to get myself in

00:33:05.120 --> 00:33:06.789
trouble. I'm like, 'Are you rebuking

00:33:08.000 --> 00:33:09.830
me?'No.

00:33:12.399 --> 00:33:13.750
You're doing great.

00:33:13.760 --> 00:33:15.909
I get nervous

00:33:15.909 --> 00:33:15.919
because

00:33:15.919 --> 00:33:17.190
I don't want to get in trouble.

00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:18.870
I'm your secretary, just

