00:46:49.109 --> 00:46:49.119
Ghost—being

00:46:49.119 --> 00:46:50.790
filled with the overflowing with

00:46:50.800 --> 00:46:52.870
the Holy Ghost. That's what I'm talking

00:46:52.880 --> 00:46:54.950
about. It's not like being drunk. I

00:46:54.960 --> 00:46:57.349
know a lot of people try to be flaky and

00:46:57.359 --> 00:46:59.589
weird about stuff, but I'm talking about

00:46:59.599 --> 00:47:01.349
