00:47:16.079 --> 00:47:19.750
showed me what he showed me about

00:47:19.760 --> 00:47:21.910
sobering days coming, and I remember even

00:47:21.920 --> 00:47:24.470
where I was looking at on the road

00:47:24.470 --> 00:47:24.480
and

00:47:24.480 --> 00:47:26.390
the tree and everything—and he told

00:47:26.400 --> 00:47:28.309
