00:48:26.720 --> 00:48:28.230
don't want to know anything

00:48:28.230 --> 00:48:28.240
else.'And

00:48:28.240 --> 00:48:30.309
so I don't like to feed on

00:48:30.319 --> 00:48:32.470
the news. Fox—I used to watch Fox a

00:48:32.480 --> 00:48:36.069
