00:48:51.280 --> 00:48:53.190
getting in the word, you know? And

00:48:53.200 --> 00:48:55.589
know that greater is he that is in

00:48:55.599 --> 00:48:57.270
you than he that is in the world. And

00:48:57.280 --> 00:48:58.870
I'm not moved by what I see. I'm not

00:48:58.880 --> 00:49:00.470
