00:49:12.960 --> 00:49:15.030
plan for me. The steps of the righteous

00:49:15.040 --> 00:49:17.910
are ordered by the Lord. And

00:49:17.920 --> 00:49:19.589
so I'm believing I'm righteous with

00:49:19.599 --> 00:49:21.349
the Lord. I'm going to be with him. I'm

00:49:21.359 --> 00:49:23.430
