00:49:39.589 --> 00:49:39.599
me.

00:49:39.599 --> 00:49:40.950
I say, "You know what, Lord? I

00:49:40.960 --> 00:49:42.790
know you're showing me this stuff, but I

00:49:42.800 --> 00:49:44.870
have the power and the ability to pray

00:49:44.880 --> 00:49:47.589
in the Holy Ghost, and I can change

00:49:47.599 --> 00:49:50.069
