00:51:19.109 --> 00:51:19.119
You

00:51:19.119 --> 00:51:21.349
have

00:51:21.359 --> 00:51:22.950
to be careful who you let put

00:51:22.950 --> 00:51:22.960
their

00:51:22.960 --> 00:51:24.630
hands on

00:51:24.630 --> 00:51:24.640
you.

00:51:24.640 --> 00:51:26.470
There

00:51:26.470 --> 00:51:26.480
are

00:51:26.480 --> 00:51:28.309
impartations, and

